  }, {
    "tStartMs": 662790,
    "dDurationMs": 2340,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "what is the actual problem to go solve?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 665130,
    "dDurationMs": 2727,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And I think, you know,\nwe see a lot of customers"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 667857,
    "dDurationMs": 2163,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and doing a lot of\nthings we love all of it,"
