  }, {
    "tStartMs": 718890,
    "dDurationMs": 2730,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Is it ready for scaled use like that?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 721620,
    "dDurationMs": 3240,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Yeah, so I think in a lot of ways it is,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 724860,
    "dDurationMs": 3900,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "in a lot of ways if you are\nin a spot where you can,"
