  }, {
    "tStartMs": 763140,
    "dDurationMs": 2700,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "with our roadmap throughout\nthe rest of the year."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 765840,
    "dDurationMs": 2580,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And one really important\nbit when we think about that"
