  }, {
    "tStartMs": 780150,
    "dDurationMs": 2280,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "because you don't have to\nwrite all that code yourself."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 782430,
    "dDurationMs": 2610,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "It's actually like, how can\nwe really, truly help you"
