  }, {
    "tStartMs": 888720,
    "dDurationMs": 1020,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Yeah, I mean, I think there's a,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 889740,
    "dDurationMs": 2820,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "so we mentioned web search and web fetch."
