  }, {
    "tStartMs": 892560,
    "dDurationMs": 3900,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I think an another big\nthing that we're seeing"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 896460,
    "dDurationMs": 4620,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "is customers right now\nhave to do a lot of work"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 901080,
    "dDurationMs": 1320,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to manage the context window."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 902400,
    "dDurationMs": 4290,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So by default, Claude has\n200 K tokens of context."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 906690,
    "dDurationMs": 4350,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "We have a million token\navailable now in beta on Sonnet,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 911040,
    "dDurationMs": 3390,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "which is great, but even a\nmillion, there's a limit there."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 914430,
    "dDurationMs": 2640,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And what many customers have told us"
