  }, {
    "tStartMs": 963720,
    "dDurationMs": 1410,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "you can focus a little bit better."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 965130,
    "dDurationMs": 2340,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So if you declutter the prompt actually,"
