  }, {
    "tStartMs": 967470,
    "dDurationMs": 2130,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "the model can actually\nfocus a little bit better."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 969600,
    "dDurationMs": 960,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Ah, interesting."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 970560,
    "dDurationMs": 2280,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So okay, we're moving unnecessary context."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 972840,
    "dDurationMs": 3240,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Is there a risk that we\nremove necessary context?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 976080,
    "dDurationMs": 1025,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Yeah.\n- How does that work?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 977105,
    "dDurationMs": 833,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Yeah, yeah, yeah."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 977938,
    "dDurationMs": 4382,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So we have some guardrails\nand some bounds around it,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 982320,
    "dDurationMs": 1870,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "but the general rule is"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 986310,
    "dDurationMs": 3750,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "we try to remove the tools\nthat are several turns back,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 990060,
    "dDurationMs": 1050,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that the model's already made decisions"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 991110,
    "dDurationMs": 2418,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "based on those tools."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 993528,
    "dDurationMs": 2082,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Yeah, I was playing with it recently"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 995610,
    "dDurationMs": 3810,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and I removed the tools\nthat it was just called"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 999420,
    "dDurationMs": 1860,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and it's, oh, my tool results are gone,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1001280,
    "dDurationMs": 833,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I don't know what to do."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1002113,
    "dDurationMs": 2317,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And then, but the model,\nthe Sonnet doesn't give up."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1004430,
    "dDurationMs": 1927,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "It's like, I'm just gonna call\nthis tool again, you know?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1006357,
    "dDurationMs": 1613,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Yeah, yeah, yeah, yeah."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1007970,
    "dDurationMs": 2070,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- But yeah, so generally we\nhave put some bounds on that,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1010040,
    "dDurationMs": 1080,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "because of that experience."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1011120,
    "dDurationMs": 2723,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So we do preserve the\nmost recent set of tools."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1013843,
    "dDurationMs": 833,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- I see, okay."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1014676,
    "dDurationMs": 3764,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- And then the other cool\nthing we do is tombstone it."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1018440,
    "dDurationMs": 4170,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So by that we mean when\nwe remove the tool calls,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1022610,
    "dDurationMs": 1920,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "we put a note in there\nto the model that say,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1024530,
    "dDurationMs": 3630,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "oh, the tool results for\nthe search call were here."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1028160,
    "dDurationMs": 1310,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Oh, okay.\n- And they've been removed."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1029470,
    "dDurationMs": 2500,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- So the model's not\ncompletely memory wiped."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1031970,
    "dDurationMs": 833,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Exactly."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1032803,
    "dDurationMs": 1957,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I think we found the model does better"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1034760,
    "dDurationMs": 2100,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "if we just give it a little more context"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1036860,
    "dDurationMs": 1353,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "about what is happening."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1039470,
    "dDurationMs": 2875,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And so that's a key feature."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1042345,
    "dDurationMs": 1565,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And the other one is"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1043910,
    "dDurationMs": 4920,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "this kind of agentic memory feature"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1048830,
    "dDurationMs": 1770,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that we've added."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1050600,
    "dDurationMs": 3030,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And there we have seen"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1053630,
    "dDurationMs": 3150,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that the model does,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1056780,
    "dDurationMs": 1830,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "right now, if you give\na task to the model,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1058610,
    "dDurationMs": 4050,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "say a deep research task\nor play Pokemon or whatnot,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1062660,
    "dDurationMs": 4200,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "the model does about the\nsame every time it runs."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1066860,
    "dDurationMs": 2340,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "But if you give a human a task,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1069200,
    "dDurationMs": 1740,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "the fifth time the human does a task,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1070940,
    "dDurationMs": 1740,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "they do it way better,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1072680,
    "dDurationMs": 1050,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "because they've learned, okay,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1073730,
    "dDurationMs": 2010,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "if I'm gonna do this search, okay,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1075740,
    "dDurationMs": 2310,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "probably the Wikipedia site is better"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1078050,
    "dDurationMs": 1770,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "than this other site or whatever."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1079820,
    "dDurationMs": 3210,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "They learn which thing, so\nthey get better over time."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1083030,
    "dDurationMs": 2760,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So we've given this memory\ntool to the model now,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1085790,
    "dDurationMs": 2790,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "so that the model can\nactually take some notes"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1088580,
    "dDurationMs": 1290,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "while it's going and say,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1089870,
    "dDurationMs": 3900,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "oh, I realize that this website\nmaybe isn't the right one,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1093770,
    "dDurationMs": 2040,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "or if I'm doing a search,\nit should be like this,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1095810,
    "dDurationMs": 2550,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "or if I'm looking up, I\nshould use this database,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1098360,
    "dDurationMs": 1890,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "not that database or whatnot."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1100250,
    "dDurationMs": 1320,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And it makes those notes."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1101570,
    "dDurationMs": 1920,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And then when it's stumped,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1103490,
    "dDurationMs": 2400,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "it can actually go back\nand review its notes"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1105890,
    "dDurationMs": 2550,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and say, okay, oh, I'm starting this task,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1108440,
    "dDurationMs": 2410,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "let me go read the notes,\nso I can figure it out."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1110850,
    "dDurationMs": 1100,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Ah, cool."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1111950,
    "dDurationMs": 2812,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So we're handling all of that\nfor the developer to say."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1114762,
    "dDurationMs": 1898,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Yeah, yeah, well, we're giving the model"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1116660,
    "dDurationMs": 2340,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "this core capability to do memory,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1119000,
    "dDurationMs": 3060,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and right now we're letting the\ndeveloper manage the memory."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1122060,
    "dDurationMs": 1770,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So, because, you know,\ndifferent developers,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1123830,
    "dDurationMs": 2580,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "they might wanna store\nit in some cloud storage"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1126410,
    "dDurationMs": 1260,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "or they might wanna\nstore it somewhere else."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1127670,
    "dDurationMs": 2250,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So we're letting developers\nfigure out exactly"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1129920,
    "dDurationMs": 1740,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "where to store the memory."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1131660,
    "dDurationMs": 2100,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "That way they have more control over that."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1134630,
    "dDurationMs": 1699,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- But exposing the tool.\n- But expose the tool."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1136329,
    "dDurationMs": 1241,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Yeah, we expose the tool."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1137570,
    "dDurationMs": 2970,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- So going back again to\na roadmap question here."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1140540,
    "dDurationMs": 2130,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So it sounds like there's\na ton of new features"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1142670,
    "dDurationMs": 1290,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that we've recently launched."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1143960,
    "dDurationMs": 900,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "There's a lot of momentum,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1144860,
    "dDurationMs": 1500,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and now there's other offerings as well,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1146360,
    "dDurationMs": 3213,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "like the Claude Code SDK\nand things coming out soon."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1150710,
    "dDurationMs": 1740,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "What are you most excited about, Katelyn?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1152450,
    "dDurationMs": 2970,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "What's the future looking like\nhere in the next 6-12 months?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1155420,
    "dDurationMs": 1590,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Yeah, so we talked a little bit about"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1157010,
    "dDurationMs": 1650,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "these higher orders of abstraction"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1158660,
    "dDurationMs": 3750,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "where we can really just make it"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1162410,
    "dDurationMs": 1560,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "as simple as possible"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1163970,
    "dDurationMs": 3150,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "for you to get the absolute\nbest outcomes out of Claude."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1167120,
    "dDurationMs": 2070,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And we wanna pair that\nwith the observability"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1169190,
    "dDurationMs": 1140,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that we talked about,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1170330,
    "dDurationMs": 1770,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "so that you can really, you know,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1172100,
    "dDurationMs": 2700,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "see the data and take those insights"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1174800,
    "dDurationMs": 2550,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "from those longer running tasks."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1177350,
    "dDurationMs": 1410,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And if you can combine\nthese things together"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1178760,
    "dDurationMs": 1770,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and start to think about\nsome of the capabilities"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1180530,
    "dDurationMs": 1980,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "like memory that Brad just talked about,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1182510,
    "dDurationMs": 1770,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "you can really start to see this flywheel"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1184280,
    "dDurationMs": 2370,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "where over time we're\nnot just able to help you"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1186650,
    "dDurationMs": 1860,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "get the best outcomes out of Claude,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1188510,
    "dDurationMs": 1950,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "but we can help you get self-improving"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1190460,
    "dDurationMs": 2730,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and continuously improving\noutcomes out of Claude."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1193190,
    "dDurationMs": 3390,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And that to me is kind\nof the galaxy brain magic"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1196580,
    "dDurationMs": 3120,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "of the roadmap is get to\na point where, you know,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1199700,
    "dDurationMs": 3000,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "we have people coming to us,\nthey're building on Claude,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1202700,
    "dDurationMs": 3210,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "they have their tasks, they\nknow what they're trying to do,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1205910,
    "dDurationMs": 2610,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and they get these really like aha moments"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1208520,
    "dDurationMs": 3780,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "where over time it's getting\nbetter and better and better."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1212300,
    "dDurationMs": 2790,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And you know, that's\nkind of the biggest thing"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1215090,
    "dDurationMs": 1320,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that in everything that we're doing,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1216410,
    "dDurationMs": 1740,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "we're trying to make\nsure we're going after."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1218150,
    "dDurationMs": 1650,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- That's awesome."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1219800,
    "dDurationMs": 1373,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Yeah, I mean, I guess I'd have to say"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1221173,
    "dDurationMs": 2587,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I'm always excited about model launches."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1223760,
    "dDurationMs": 1890,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "It's like Christmas, wow,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1225650,
    "dDurationMs": 2460,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "what will be possible now?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1228110,
    "dDurationMs": 2010,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So I love playing with the model launches"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1230120,
    "dDurationMs": 2850,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "they come out, just\nunlocks more use cases,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1232970,
    "dDurationMs": 3000,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "some use cases that, you know,\nwe've been working hard on"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1235970,
    "dDurationMs": 2730,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and trying to improve,\nwhich is satisfying to see,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1238700,
    "dDurationMs": 2340,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "but also some things I\nhad no idea the model"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1241040,
    "dDurationMs": 1260,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "would be able to do this thing."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1242300,
    "dDurationMs": 3210,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "You know, now it draws ASCII\npictures so much better"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1245510,
    "dDurationMs": 1470,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "or what, you know, whatever."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1246980,
    "dDurationMs": 2010,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- The important things.\n- Very important things."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1248990,
    "dDurationMs": 2610,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "But beyond that, the other\nthing I'm really excited about"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1251600,
    "dDurationMs": 4950,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "is we're in the early stages\nof giving Claude a computer."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1256550,
    "dDurationMs": 2910,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "You know, I think about\nif we hire an employee"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1259460,
    "dDurationMs": 1957,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "here at Anthropic and we welcome 'em,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1261417,
    "dDurationMs": 923,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "\"Here's your first day.\""
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1262340,
    "dDurationMs": 2100,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "But we don't give them a computer."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1264440,
    "dDurationMs": 2880,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "They would not be very\nsuccessful at Anthropic."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1267320,
    "dDurationMs": 3450,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So right now, essentially\neverybody is using Claude"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1270770,
    "dDurationMs": 1620,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and it doesn't have a computer."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1272390,
    "dDurationMs": 2847,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So I'm really excited about\ngiving Claude a computer"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1275237,
    "dDurationMs": 3333,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and you see the very baby steps of that"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1278570,
    "dDurationMs": 2250,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "with the code execution tool,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1280820,
    "dDurationMs": 4110,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "where the model can write\ncode executed on the VM"
    } ]
  }, {
